## Context
Implement a reusable scroll lock hook for the chat message list. Requirements:
1. Auto-scroll to bottom while AI is streaming
2. Stop auto-scrolling if user scrolls up (reading earlier content)
3. Resume auto-scrolling when user scrolls back near the bottom (within 100px)
4. Force-scroll to bottom on stream completion regardless of lock state

## Implementation
**Location:** `apps/ui/src/hooks/use-scroll-lock.ts`

```tsx
import { useRef, useEffect, useCallback, useLayoutEffect } from 'react';

export function useScrollLock() {
  const containerRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);
  const lockedRef = useRef(true);

  useEffect(() => {
    const el = containerRef.current;
    if (!el) return;

    const onScroll = () => {
      const distanceFromBottom = el.scrollHeight - el.scrollTop - el.clientHeight;
      lockedRef.current = distanceFromBottom < 100;
    };

    el.addEventListener('scroll', onScroll, { passive: true });
    return () => el.removeEventListener('scroll', onScroll);
  }, []);

  const scrollToBottom = useCallback((force = false) => {
    const el = containerRef.current;
    if (!el) return;
    if (force || lockedRef.current) {
      el.scrollTop = el.scrollHeight;
    }
  }, []);

  return { containerRef, scrollToBottom };
}
```

**IMPORTANT:** The caller must use `useLayoutEffect` (not `useEffect`) to trigger `scrollToBottom()` after content updates — `useEffect` fires after paint, causing a one-frame lag.

```tsx
// Usage in message list component:
const { containerRef, scrollToBottom } = useScrollLock();

useLayoutEffect(() => {
  scrollToBottom();
}, [content, scrollToBottom]);

useLayoutEffect(() => {
  if (isComplete) scrollToBottom(true);
}, [isComplete, scrollToBottom]);
```

Wire the hook into the chat message list container. Replace any existing scroll-to-bottom logic.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Hook exported from `apps/ui/src/hooks/use-scroll-lock.ts`
- Auto-scrolls while streaming
- Stops auto-scrolling when user scrolls up more than 100px from bottom
- Resumes when user scrolls back near bottom
- Force-scrolls on stream completion
- Uses useLayoutEffect at call sites (not useEffect)
- No TypeScript errors

